# Highest Waves - Padding Structure Guidelines

## Overview
This document defines the comprehensive padding and spacing structure for the Highest Waves project. All components must follow these patterns to ensure consistent spacing across all screen sizes and zoom levels.

## Screen Size Breakpoints

### Mobile First Approach
- **Mobile**: 320px - 639px
- **Small Tablet**: 640px - 767px  
- **Tablet**: 768px - 1023px
- **Desktop**: 1024px - 1279px
- **Large Desktop**: 1280px - 1535px
- **TV/Large Screens**: 1536px+

