## Grid System Patterns

### Responsive Grid
```css
.page-grid-1 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
.page-grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
.page-grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
.page-grid-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }

/* Small tablets */
@media (min-width: 640px) {
  .page-grid-2, .page-grid-3, .page-grid-4 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
}

/* Tablets */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .page-grid-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; }
  .page-grid-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 2rem; }
}

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .page-grid-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2.5rem; }
}

/* Large screens */
@media (min-width: 1280px) {
  .page-grid-1, .page-grid-2, .page-grid-3, .page-grid-4 { gap: 3rem; }
}

/* TV/Large screens */
@media (min-width: 1536px) {
  .page-grid-1, .page-grid-2, .page-grid-3, .page-grid-4 { gap: 3.5rem; }
}
```

