### Container Constraints
```css
/* Prevent horizontal overflow on zoom */
.page-container {
  overflow-x: hidden;
  width: 100%;
}

/* Ensure content remains readable on zoom */
.page-content-wrapper {
  max-width: 1400px;
  margin: 0 auto;
